high_descs: Move across  the grey room to the black stand that the TV is on.
Pick up the keys that are by the newspaper.
Turn around and move across the blue room to the sofa.
Place the keys on the right hand side of the remote that is on the sofa.
Move across the blue room into the yellow room until you are in front of the three black stands.  You want to move to the middle stand.
Pick up the keys that are on far left side toward the back of the middle black stand.
Turn around and cross through the yellow room to the blue room.  Move to the couch.
Place the keys near the front of the left sofa cushion.
anns.task_desc: Move 2 sets of keys from 2 different rooms to the couch in the blue room.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the rug on the floor, and walk to the dress on your right with the TV on it.
Take the keys from the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the couch.
Put the keys on the couch next to the remote control.
Turn left and walk towards the fireplace, turn left again and walk to the end table with the keys on it.
Pick up one set of keys from the end table.
Turn around and walk to the couch behind you.
Put the keys on the couch near the green cushion.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the TV stand
Grab the keys off of the stand

Put the keys on the sofa

anns.task_desc: Putting two sets of keys on the sofa
